Multimap<String, String>`.\n  - Verifies sorted keys, sorted values, equality, and restored comparators.\n  - This should exercise the remaining `TreeMultimap.writeObject` and `TreeMultimap.readObject` dynamic-access call sites.\n\n- Updated `tests/src/org.glassfish.jersey.bundles.repackaged/jersey-guava/2.23.2/src/test/resources/META-INF/native-image/reachability-metadata.json`\n  - Added Native Image serialization registrations for:\n    - `jersey.repackaged.com.google.common.collect.TreeMultimap`\n    - `jersey.repackaged.com.google.common.collect.NaturalOrdering`\n\nTests were not run, per instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06a56e79ed7a4f310169f542835c64819481959b480288ab6b\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 871, "output": 741, "cacheRead": 23552, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 25164, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777681017681, "responseId": "resp_06a56e79ed7a4f310169f5427a295881948ab1a3bcc096dbc6"}, "toolResults": []}
